            <li>@Html.ActionLink("Products", "Index", "Products")</li>
            <li>@Html.ActionLink("Suppliers", "Index", "Suppliers")</li>
        </ul>
        
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Live Client Project</h2>
        <p>Over half of the class is a live client project using the tools and techniques taught in the first half of the semester. The project proceeds through a series of Sprints, each with its own planning, development, review and retorspective stages.</p>
    </div>
</div>